# modules/run.list 
# list for run all modules function one by one

##### file work flow #####

# id|title|function|enabled|mandatory

# id : function script id
# title : title abuot function 
# function : a function in sourced modules
# enabled : yes or no for chose what do you want to run 

# mandatory : yes or no for mange price to run
# - this is used for sort requirments or not requirments function
# - yes : means this is important and error if failed
# - no : means this isn't important and skip to run if failed

##### run modules #####


build|Build environment setup|main_build_setup|yes|yes

flatpak|flatpak repo builder|main_flatpak|yes|no

build|build|main_build|yes|yes

